OL,3,CGalashiels Academy 'progressing well'
OL,4,Cas new school set to be open in 2025
OL,6,FScottish Borders Council has said that
OL,7,FGalashiels Academy is "progressing
OL,8,Fwell" and that the project "remains on
OL,9,Ftrack" and will be open to students by
OL,10,FAutumn 2025.
OL,12,FConstruction began on the project in
OL,13,FJuly 2023 with the aim of creating a
OL,14,Fmodern, flexible learning environment
OL,15,Fwhich will also included spaces that
OL,16,Fcan be utilised by the wider community.
