OL,6,FOutside of the existing school
OL,7,Fbuilding there are information boards
OL,8,Fby the contractor which will share
OL,9,Finformation about the project and the
OL,10,Fcommunity engagement undertaken.
OL,12,FThe council state that the building
OL,13,Fhas been designed to encourage
OL,14,Fcollaboration, creativity and
OL,15,Fsocialising.
