OL,6,FA range of new sports facilities are
OL,7,Fset to be included as part of the
OL,8,Fbuild which features a swimming pool,
OL,9,F2G hockey pitch, 3G rugby and football
OL,10,Fpitch, grass football pitch, tennis
OL,11,Fcourts and a 100m running track.
OL,13,FCouncillor Leagh Douglas, Executive
OL,14,FMember for Education & Lifelong
OL,15,FLearning, said: "After almost a year
OL,16,Fof construction completed on the new
OL,17,Freplacement for Academy, I am
OL,18,Fdelighted to see the physical building
OL,19,Fbegin to take shape.
